<D>__{who's there?}
<A>__{on the far side of the room, a movement in the shadows. julia almost retreats, but something keeps her staring into the murk, as something the remnants of a human form made of twisted, blistered strands of flesh, raises its head. it's squatting against the wall, unable to lift itself into a standing position. its eyes, however, have life in them: and hunger. this, though he's unrecognizable, is frank.}
